  <p>
I also really wanted to show that anybody could be a leader or take on a leadership role. 

I wanted to demonstrate that you don't need to be the most confident person, or the loudest person in the room.

And that leadership takes many forms so quieter or less confident people can still lead team’s successfully.

</p>


