<p>
To me, leadership is all about people 

and creating a safe and trusting environment so that everyone in the team can do their best work. 

Luis Romero described leaders who successfully build that trust as being willing to be vulnerable, sharing their weaknesses and struggles to create a sense of safety in their teams. 

</p>

