They also describe what it means to be vulnerable as..</p>
<ul class="unordered-list">
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item">being authentic</li>
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item">embracing discomfort</li>
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item">admitting mistakes</li>
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item">and listening actively and openly</li>
  </ul>

<p>
Working in this way creates collacollaberotive, creative, and successful teams.
</p>

