<p>
The conclusion I drew form all of this was that to lead successfully in a large organisation I needed to change the way I behaved.

This is summed up nicely by Yukl and Mahsud who wrote..</p>
<p>
“flexible and adaptive leadership involves changing behavior in appropriate ways as the situation changes”. 

</p>
  
